Whether you’re new to prayer or have been praying your whole life, it can sometimes feel overwhelming figuring out where to begin. Maybe the idea of praying has you panicked. Maybe you’re just unsure of where to start. That’s okay!

Inside this prayer guide, you’ll find examples of how to pray when life feels heavy, how to ask God for help, and how to find peace through prayer.

You'll also find simple, powerful prayers for strength, hope, stress, and more. These prayers are designed to be honest, approachable, and easy to use—no perfect words required.

Whether you’re praying for emotional strength, spiritual endurance, or just enough energy to get through the day, this guide will help you talk to God in a way that's real and personal.
